info.author: Samuel Fekete
info.description:
PeasyPy
=======

*Python development environment for children.*

PeasyPy makes it really easy for children to get started with coding from a very young age.

Project status
--------------
This project is currently at a very early prototype stage.

Credits
-------
Some images are taken from or derived from images on:
- openclipart.org
- pixabay.com
